==History==
The Cocoon station model was originally commissioned for the purpose of research into the biology of the xenonids. 
after an incident on 12/██/████, on station PCS #005. Within one of the storage sections of the facility contained behind the laboratory that on the girders within, that certain construction methods of the girders led to the xenonids utilizing it in the construction of their structures. This was then later applied to the station bridge when it was destroyed by a large scale impact of an meteorite, by the construction office of Penguin Corporation. The chitin fused with the framework that was constructed, fusing into the remaining sections of the asteroid.

