==Contractional obligations==
Due to the nature of the contracts regarding maintenance and repair, Nanotressen personnel aren't allowed to do in-depth long term maintenance without getting a permitting hand from the company to approve it. due to this, most modifications are reverted shortly after staffing personnel leave, most added machines are shuffled off to higher end stations.

===Biological Sculpting Program===
A major part of the station relies on the knowledge that Penguin corp has gathered with sculpting the Xenological sections of the station. Due to insistence (and sheer financial cost) on Nanotressen personnel being unable to record or be onboard while specialists who coax the living sections of the station to self repair; Nanotressen is completely at the whim of Penguin Corporation to continue servicing the handful of retrofitted instances of the station. Due to this shifts are completely limited to five hours to give Maintenance personnel proper time to clean the station up and revert any unwarranted modifications, after which specialists arrive from Penguin corp to feed the station and Sculpt repairs back into the station.